nodes.title: Positive
widgets_values: A silver haired man with a orange butterfly on his finger, turns his head towards the viewer, the butterfly flies away top left of frame, as the man lowers his hand to rest naturally at his side, as he starts to walk forward. The wind blowing his shirt as he moves forward. The camera tracks the man. The blue butterflies flutter in the background.
